## Auto Context Load

### Default Load (Always)

```
1. CLAUDE.md
2. .context/WORKFLOW.md
3. .context/sprints/s{current}/context.md
```

### Conditional Load (Pattern Matching)

| Detected Pattern | Auto-Load |
|-----------------|----------|
{{#each domains}}
| `{{name}}` related pattern | `{{path}}*.md` |
{{/each}}
| `PRD`, `기획서/spec doc` | `templates/prd.md` |
| `검증/validation`, `Before/After` | `templates/validation-report.md` |
| `회고/retrospective` | `templates/retrospective.md` |
| `핸드오프/handoff` | `templates/story-v2.md` |
| `Guard Rail` | `templates/guardrail.md` |

### Smart Context Chaining

```
[PRD Authoring] templates/prd.md → global/strategy.md → sprints/s{N}/context.md
[Validation Request] templates/validation-report.md → templates/guardrail.md → relevant PRD
[Retrospective Request] templates/retrospective.md → sprints/s{N}/context.md → results.md
```

